These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, water, 7up, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people have 6 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, sudoku, reading, traveling, baking
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | mirinda  | water    | 7up  | sprite      | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby      | filmmaking  | baking | traveling | cooking | reading | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero, martial-arts, horror, western, musical
6 different pets are kept: pony, snake, cat, horse, chinchilla, fish
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the fish##1
8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | western | superhero | musical | horror     | martial-arts  |
| Pet           | cat | snake    | pony      | fish  | horse | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, pop, folk, d&b, metal, rock
There are 6 different nationalities: indian, egyptian, turkish, canadian, brazilian, italian
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of folk is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the fan of metal is on the right of the italian##1
6. the fan of metal is on the left of the egyptian##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the turkish is the fan of d&b##1
9. the fan of folk is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | rock   | metal      | pop | ambient  | folk   |
| Nationality   | turkish | italian | indian | egyptian   | brazilian | canadian |

