.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: d&b, techno, ambient, soul, r&b, rock
The people use 6 different means of transport: tram, scooter, jet-ski, motorbike, subway, van
1. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
5. the person driving the van is the fan of soul##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul | d&b      | techno  | rock | r&b |
| Transport     | tram | van  | subway | jet-ski | motorbike  | scooter    |

