.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, sudoku, dancing, board-games, cooking
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: folk, reggae, hip-hop, blues, punk, jazz
 1. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 3. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 5. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of blues##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | dancing | cooking | puzzles | board-games | rock-climbing | sudoku  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | blues  | hip-hop  | folk | punk      | reggae |

