.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: potato, lime, corn, spinach, garlic, asparagus
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts, adventure, romance, musical, time-travel
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating lime##1
4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating asparagus is the person watching fantasy movies##1
8. the person eating corn is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | lime | asparagus   | garlic  | corn    | spinach  | potato |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | fantasy | time-travel | musical | adventure | romance |

