.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, soy-milk, milk, water, hot-chocolate
The people have 6 different jobs:  hot-chocolatecher, security-guard, videographer, accountant, architect, chef
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
