3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
4. the videographer is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the security-guard is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking cola is the accountant##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the architect is on the left of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | cola     | soy-milk | iced-tea | milk | water   |
| Job        | chef | accountant | architect | videographer   | hot-chocolatecher    | security-guard |

