4. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | goldfish       | horse   | frog      | chinchilla | mouse          |
| Sport   | sailing | surfing | biathlon | climbing | rowing | water-polo |

